name: Eleanor's Notebook
description:
Captain John Franklin disappeared during his fourth expedition in the Arctic. Her daughter Eleanor tries to find some clues and found some from the local Inuits. Stories treasured in her notebook she might find the vessel of her father. But Carlota Clementine stole it from her. She has to run into the endless white snow filled with icy obstacles to retrieve the only thing that can help her in her quest.

Use keys 1-2-3-4 and press the one that appears over the symbol before the timer runs out.
